      "id": "bb069b8e-857f-410e-b223-85b52463ea4b",
      "title": "[VERIFIED-NO-CODE] [Fix] Completion-Flow für Research-/QA-Artefakte trotz Security-Gate sauber machen",
      "description": "Task ID: TASK-COMPLETION-SECURITY-GATE-FLOW\n\nObjective: Fix the task completion flow so valid research/QA artifact tasks can be closed cleanly or classified correctly without getting stuck in an inappropriate security gate path.\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- Reproduce why the retrieval smokepack task could not complete cleanly and fell into security-check-failed / blocked\n- Distinguish genuine risky completion paths from low-risk research/QA artifact completion paths\n- Implement the smallest safe fix so these tasks can end in the correct terminal state\n- Keep security protections intact for actually risky task types\n\nReturn format:\n- EXECUTION_STATUS\n- RESULT_SUMMARY",
      "status": "in-progress",
      "priority": "low",
      "assigned_agent": "Forge",
      "project": "Mission Control",
      "createdAt": "2026-04-11T07:26:46.831Z",
